lyTime":"2018-04-08T03:56:54.000Z","msg":"罰款800元<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">狗都吠啦</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"943e1d119459318e33df494058d338b68c72f964","tid":621041,"uid":77547,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T03:57:53.000Z","msg":"至少釀成兩死五傷，當中包括護犬女狗主<br />\n^---以為狗主死左"},{"pid":"0f5e0e10b7ebfef4b01aaac6913b94fa611a8bfc","tid":621041,"uid":65128,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T03:59:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54536365265606af4e786399407eb0274cf65254","tid":621041,"uid":45847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T03:59:09.000Z","msg":"條狗被人咬死冇懲罰<br />\n係我真係毆死條狗話佢撞牆死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e2556bdea0645ee0f61f0ae1ead01033339df1","tid":621041,"uid":5651,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0cfeebd86a3d00f6f60b3b0a5911601872935ebf","tid":621041,"uid":166709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T03:45:23.000Z","msg":"罰款800元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T04:00:00.000Z","msg":"仆街 亂拋垃圾都罰1500<br />\n屌你隻狗亂咬其他狗罰800<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34162b486606551617302720f333c48cc18a93b1","tid":621041,"uid":50818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T04:02:58.000Z","msg":"有D養開狗既人會當隻狗係家庭成員之一黎<br />\n佢俾人咬死，既然法律幫唔到佢，就諗方法自己報仇喇"},{"pid":"f50d5d38ecc387d2bcd0edbade03965064802c06","tid":621041,"uid":24910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"27e2556bdea0645ee0f61f0ae1ead01033339df1","tid":621041,"uid":5651,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0cfeebd86a3d00f6f60b3b0a5911601872935ebf","tid":621041,"uid":166709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T03:45:23.000Z","msg":"罰款800元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T04:00:00.000Z","msg":"仆街 亂拋垃圾都罰1500<br />\n屌你隻狗亂咬其他狗罰800<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T04:07:07.000Z","msg":"亂拋朱古力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85eeb0239ec5234e662815ac3e8d4db4d6ab253f","tid":621041,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T04:12:55.000Z","msg":"貝澳近海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a14b3c91b067c297e72bddc75c104d72b413d3","tid":621041,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T04:16:21.000Z","msg":"如果係防爆格, 有冇需要養17隻狗咁多?"},{"pid":"20f7b7c698e8cb7fa055032476d59d4ec36cf66d","tid":621041,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T04:20:10.000Z","msg":"反社會毒狗人士 希望你地睇到新聞後做返件好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}